name: Pennzoil ATF Dexron VI

localDocs.name: Pzl ATF Dexron VI United States English
Pzl ATF Dexron VI United States EN 140002686046 EHS V5.0 05-JUL-2019

marketing: PENNZOIL^® Dexron[sup]^®[/sup] -VI Automatic Transmission Fluid is an exceptional automatic transmission fluid approved by General Motors for use in vehicles with automatic transmissions. It is specially formulated to provide twice the service life of a Dexron[sup]^®[/sup]-III(H) ATF and offers enhanced performance for both new and older transmissions. It is designed to protect transmissions through improved oxidation resistance, friction durability, shear stability and wear protection to help meet warranty protection requirements in late model vehicles.
